description:
2005 movie - "Wallis & Edward"

DivX TVRip [English]

In 1936, England and the Commonwealth were shaken with the news that Edward VIII, King of England, was in love with American divorcee Wallis Simpson. The establishment deemed her an unsuitable wife for a monarch and their ensuing romance lead to a constitutional crisis in the United Kingdom and ultimately to Edward's abdication from the throne.

Joely Richardson (Nip/Tuck) and Steven Campbell Moore (A Good Woman) star as Simpson and Edward VIII.
